    "en": {
      "title": "Sathosa's 5 Essential Foods Price Dropped",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lanka Sathosa has immediately reduced the price of five essential food items from today (23), said a senior official of Lanka Sathosa.",
        "Accordingly, the price of Ponni Samba rice has been reduced by 21 rupees to 194 rupees, a kilo of lentils has been reduced by 25 rupees to 460 rupees, a kilo of horse mackerel has been reduced by 25 rupees to 1,375 rupees, and a kilo of imported Nadu rice has been reduced to 2 rupees. The official further said that the price of brown sugar was reduced by 2 rupees to 310 rupees."
      ],
